# The upstream CardioTox repo (code + ~216 MB of trained TF checkpoints) is cloned on first use into
# vendor/CardioTox at the pinned commit (see run.py::_ensure_vendor + README). Weights are NEVER committed
# (CLAUDE.md 0: never commit weights/data). The whole vendor tree is fetched on the box, so ignore it all.
vendor/CardioTox/

# isolated pixi env (the box-solved lock is committed; the env itself is not)
.pixi/
